**`pkg/jira/client.go`** — added `GetSprintIssueKeys(ctx, sprintID)` with automatic pagination through `/rest/agile/1.0/sprint/{id}/issue`.

**`internal/adapters/jiraadpt/jiraadpt.go`** — `JiraAdapter` implementing `jirasvc.JiraEnricher`:
